  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流图。核心是从ContentCDN开始，教育资源先发送到课堂服务，然后触发成绩同步流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ContentCDN作为起点，用箭头指向ClassroomService。这条边上需要标注什么？是简单的数据发送吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标注\"Envia datos\"，西班牙语里表示发送数据。然后ClassroomService要通过HTTP请求去调GradeSync服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ClassroomService到GradeSync画好了，标注\"Petició HTTP\"。接下来GradeSync要做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync需要先验证数据，所以要连到StudentDB，标注\"Valida datos\"。然后StudentDB要查询数据，这里有个细节——查询之后还要把结果返回给GradeSync处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，GradeSync到StudentDB是验证，然后StudentDB查询数据再返回给GradeSync？那GradeSync要出现两次吗？还是循环回来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，需要两个GradeSync节点。C是GradeSync，D是StudentDB，E是另一个GradeSync。D到E标注\"Consulta datos\"，E返回D标注\"Responde datos\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，StudentDB到GradeSync的往返。现在数据流要回到C节点吗？从D返回C？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，D返回C，标注\"Devuelve datos\"。然后C要返回HTTP响应给B，最后B处理完数据还要回到ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C到B标注\"Respuesta HTTP\"，B到F标注\"Datos procesados\"。这里F是另一个ContentCDN节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我检查一下——F应该是ContentCDN，但A已经是ContentCDN了。让我重新理一下：A和F都是ContentCDN，但A是源节点，F是处理后的目标节点，这样画没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，A和F代表ContentCDN在不同阶段的状态。整个流程是：CDN发数据→课堂服务→成绩同步→数据库验证查询→逐级返回→最终回到CDN。这样结构清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
